h century, first for bombs and then to power submarines. The United States led the effort to generate electricity from this new source. Yet in the mid-20th century as societies began the transition to nuclear power and away from fossil fuels, a long-term PR campaign to scare the public began, funded in part by coal and oil interests.','Time to look again','https://www.nuclearnowfilm.com/','2023-04-28',0,26.484,7.444,9,'/vdxG11NGlnDUWoSjRRkDKXh34ee.jpg'),(1006462,'[{\"id\": 28, \"name\": \"Action\"}, {\"id\": 9648, \"name\": \"Mystery\"}, {\"id\": 53, \"name\": \"Thriller\"}, {\"id\": 27, \"name\": \"Horror\"}]','The Flood','A horde of giant hungry alligators is unleashed on a group of in-transit prisoners and their guards after a massive hurricane floods Louisiana.','Danger is rising.','','2023-07-14',0,157.475,6.6,228,'/mvjqqklMpHwOxc40rn7dMhGT0Fc.jpg'),(1007826,'[{\"id\": 35, \"name\": \"Comedy\"}]','The Underdoggs','Jaycen \'Two Js\' Jennings is a washed-up former pro football star who has hit rock bottom. When sentenced to community service coaching the Underdoggs, an unruly pee-wee football team in his hometown, he sees it mostly as an opportunity to rebuild his public image. But in the process, he may just turn his life around and rediscover his love of the game.','From blunts to runts.','https://www.primevideo.com/detail/0P56RT24GVXUQGQKRKHRXUCK33','2024-01-25',0,212.612,6.514,74,'/wj1VRcVsh39nkxLkZP8tuGd96tc.jpg'),(1008042,'[{\"id\": 27, \"name\": \"Horror\"}, {\"id\": 53, \"name\": \"Thriller\"}]','Talk to Me','When a group of friends discover how to conjure spirits using an embalmed hand, they become hooked on the new thrill, until one of them goes too far and unleashes terrifying supernatural forces.','You call. They\'ll answer.','https://umbrellaent.com.au/movie/talk-to-me','2023-07-26',0,134.219,7.204,2276,'/kdPMUMJzyYAc4roD52qavX0nLIC.jpg'),(1008148,'[{\"id\": 10770, \"name\": \"TV Movie\"}, {\"id\": 35, \"name\": \"Comedy\"}, {\"id\": 10749, \"name\":